---
import LegalLayout from '../layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
const lang = 'en';
---

<LegalLayout lang={lang} title="Refund Policy" description="Veilus refund policy for subscription plans and lifetime deals." lastUpdated="March 6, 2026">

<h2>1. Overview</h2>
<p>We want you to be satisfied with Veilus. If you're not happy with your purchase, we offer refunds under the following conditions.</p>

<h2>2. Free Tier</h2>
<p>The Veilus Free plan is free forever (5 profiles, no time limit). No payment is required, so no refund is applicable.</p>

<h2>3. Monthly Subscriptions</h2>
<table>
  <thead>
    <tr><th>Condition</th><th>Refund</th></tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td>Within 7 days of purchase (first billing cycle)</td><td>Full refund</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Within 7 days of renewal (subsequent cycles)</td><td>Prorated refund for unused days</td></tr>
    <tr><td>After 7 days</td><td>No refund; subscription active until end of billing period</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h2>4. Annual Subscriptions</h2>
<table>
  <thead>
    <tr><th>Condition</th><th>Refund</th></tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr><td>Within 14 days of purchase</td><td>Full refund</td></tr>
    <tr><td>After 14 days, before 3 months</td><td>Prorated refund minus 20% processing fee</td></tr>
    <tr><td>After 3 months</td><td>No refund; subscription active until end of annual period</td></tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<h2>5. Lifetime Deals (AppSumo / Promotions)</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Lifetime deals purchased through third-party platforms (e.g., AppSumo) are subject to that platform's refund policy.</li>
  <li>Lifetime deals purchased directly from Veilus are <strong>non-refundable</strong> after 14 days. This is clearly stated at the time of purchase.</li>
</ul>

<h2>6. Enterprise Plans</h2>
<p>Enterprise plans are subject to individual contract terms. Refund conditions are specified in your enterprise agreement.</p>

<h2>7. How to Request a Refund</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Email <a href="mailto:billing@veilus.io">billing@veilus.io</a> with your account email and reason for the refund.</li>
  <li>We will review your request within <strong>2 business days</strong>.</li>
  <li>Approved refunds are processed within <strong>5-10 business days</strong> to the original payment method.</li>
</ol>

<h2>8. Non-Refundable Situations</h2>
<p>Refunds are <strong>not</strong> available when:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Your account was suspended or terminated due to a violation of our <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a>.</li>
  <li>You have already received a refund for a previous billing cycle.</li>
  <li>The refund request is made after the applicable refund window.</li>
  <li>You have used the Service extensively during the refund period (e.g., created 50+ profiles, executed automation at scale).</li>
</ul>

<h2>9. Downgrades Instead of Cancellation</h2>
<p>Before requesting a refund, consider downgrading to the Free tier. You'll keep your existing profiles (up to 5) and can upgrade again anytime.</p>

<h2>10. Contact</h2>
<p>For billing and refund questions:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:billing@veilus.io">billing@veilus.io</a></li>
  <li><strong>Response time:</strong> Within 2 business days</li>
</ul>

</LegalLayout>
